banipal</span>, </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">rey de Asiria que llevó el Imperio Asirio a su máxima expansión</span>, </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">llegando a conquistar incluso Babilonia</span>, </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">Egipto y Elam</span>, </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">y cuyo poderío militar y político se reflejó también en un auge en la ciencia y la cultura.</span></p><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\"></span></p>"},{"id":"peshitta-notas-1847","title":"Esdras 4:12","author":"Instituto Cultural Álef y Tau, A.C.","reference":{"book":"EZR","chapterStart":4,"verseStart":12,"chapterEnd":4,"verseEnd":12},"content":"<span style=\"color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><sup>a</sup></span> </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b14.36.13'>2Cr 36:13</a></span></p></span></p>"},{"id":"peshitta-notas-1848","title":"Esdras 4:20","author":"Instituto Cultural Álef y Tau, A.C.","reference":{"book":"EZR","chapterStart":4,"verseStart":20,"chapterEnd":4,"verseEnd":20},"content":"<span style=\"color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><sup>a</sup></span> </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b10.8.2'>2Sa 8:2</a></span>; </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b12.18.7'>2Re 18:7</a></span>; </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b12.24.20'>2Re 24:20</a></span>; </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b14.36.13'>2Cr 36:13</a></span></p></span></p>"},{"id":"peshitta-notas-1849","title":"Esdras 5:1","author":"Instituto Cultural Álef y Tau, A.C.","reference":{"book":"EZR","chapterStart":5,"verseStart":1,"chapterEnd":5,"verseEnd":1},"content":"<span style=\"color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><sup>a</sup></span> </span><span style=\"color:#